A Chado RESTful Python API.

Herein lies a server built on Ropy (which itself strings together 
CherryPy, Cheetah and psycopg2), allowing rapid prototyping 
of chado-related queries. 

Requires Python 2.5+.

PS - the fontage above is http://www.network-science.de/ascii/ | colossal.